						<p class="col2span">GeoFields, a recognized leader of managed data solutions for the oil and gas pipeline industry, is seeking talented GIS software engineers / developers. The successful candidate should have experience with C#, Esri ArcObjects, and be versed with newer Microsoft.NET Framework technologies. This position requires an individual with strong communication and collaboration skills as well as excellent coding habits including code documentation, unit testing, and the ability to follow specifications and coding standards.</p>
